description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '15-Minute Guided Meditation to Reset Your Nervous System' from the channel Caren Hope.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Join me for a 15-minute guided meditation to reset your nervous system through some simple techniques that tone the vagus nerve. You can practice this guided meditation seated or lying down. You'll be placing your hands on different parts of your body and breathing easily. Over-the-ear headphones will make the first part of this meditation difficult to practice, so I recommend no headphones or using earbuds. No prior meditation or yoga experience required. Practice anytime you would like to quickly calm or balance your mind and body.
